Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:41.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:08.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:10.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.04,0:02:13.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're a half-demon, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:16.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! If you're gonna kill me,\ndo it quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:20.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A half-demon's power is good nourishment\nfor the Human-faced Fruit Tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:24.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks to you, it'll bear\nthe Fruit of Longevity more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.46,0:02:25.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.66,0:02:29.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So hurry and get your demon\npowers back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, struggle more!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If the thorns pierce your skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:36.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,it'll make it that much easier\nto extract your juices.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:37.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the bottle in which Kagome kept\nthe Shikon Jewel Shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:50.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:53.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's the owner of the\NSacred Jewel Shards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.29,0:02:57.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Owner?\NThere ain't such a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.02,0:02:59.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found these.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:02.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't kid around!\NYou stole them from Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:03.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.86,0:03:06.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The girl who had\nthe Sacred Jewel Shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:10.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... a girl?\NWhat great news!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Somewhere in this house\nis a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:21.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tree of Human-faced Fruit loves\nwomen, too. The younger, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome... I'll be there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.25,0:03:29.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't get caught until\NI come for you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:33.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I found the shards around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.53,0:03:36.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! So you're in my box garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.47,0:03:43.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, I'm ready over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:49.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.31,0:03:52.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:54.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm ready anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.55,0:03:59.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're they up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fox fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It worked, Miroku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.53,0:04:15.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We did it! It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good, good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A young girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.84,0:04:53.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A bit dirty, but sure to please\nthe human-faced tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:54.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:58.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is the sage, Tokajin?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:00.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This has been a fine day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:05.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,An unusual half-demon and a young girl...\nall in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:09.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By tomorrow, I should have\nthe Fruit of Longevity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:11.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you see Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:15.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!\NIs Inuyasha all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:17.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive you if\nhe's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:20.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's talking to him\nand she's not afraid at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.64,0:05:24.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Comes from experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:32.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pipe down!\NGo to sleep for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:36.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,K-Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:40.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shucks! My hands are covered\nwith dirt now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! I can't stand it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is why a human body\nis so!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:55.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn! I've lost too much blood.\NI'm getting dizzy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Still alive, huh, half-demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:05.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome's clothes!\NShe couldn't be!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Kagome...\NWhere's the girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Because you broke my gourd,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:14.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,extracting nourishment\nhas become very bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.79,0:06:16.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Extract nourishment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:18.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What'd you do with Kagome?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:26.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you were in love with that\ndirt-covered girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll see her soon...\ninside my belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.24,0:06:33.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Both of you will become the\NFruit of Longevity,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.61,0:06:35.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and will be eaten by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:38.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:42.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:44.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those thorny roots cannot\nbe torn apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:47.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:51.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Being this small, I don't know how\neffective my Wind Tunnel will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:52.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.88,0:07:13.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:19.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome is in the cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.99,0:07:21.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this sweet smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:36.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.87,0:07:40.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:42.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's alive!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! These are mere scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:09.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's torn up, but wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:12.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:18.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:23.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's a mortal right now,\nyet he tried to do so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.35,0:08:28.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... we're here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.40,0:08:40.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:48.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha seems to\nbe in bad shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His injuries are pretty serious.\NWe really shouldn't move him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.21,0:08:55.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think we can get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.72,0:08:57.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you walk, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.52,0:09:01.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Out? Is it morning yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, it's pitch dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:04.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You don't intend to fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:06.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:07.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.19,0:09:09.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until your powers return,\nwe have to keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must protect everyone\nuntil day breaks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can't jump...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:31.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...Can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:37.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Plus we have to get Miroku\nand Shippo back to normal size.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.39,0:09:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:39.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:44.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You want me to escape alone, right?\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you escape from\nthe box garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.61,0:09:54.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:58.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed to admit it...\NI was Tokajin's teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then you're a sage, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.61,0:10:02.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.48,0:10:04.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why'd you make a guy like\nhim a sage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:05.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:09.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't make him a sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:11.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was the Tree of\NHuman-faced Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:13.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tree of Human-faced Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:18.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was about a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:24.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh boy... I can't stand this\ntraining day in and day out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:29.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't there some way I can\nbecome a sage right away?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:33.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hah! Nothing to eat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.12,0:10:42.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, a Sacred Jewel Shard!\NThank you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who said that?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am the Tree of Human-faced Fruit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:52.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}You there... Do you wish for\na sage's power?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:54.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:59.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then eat the fruit of the\NHuman-faced Fruit Tree.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:08.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then we shall both possess\nthe art of Sagery!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.65,0:11:12.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes! Swallow the seed, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:16.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you shall have power...\na sage's power!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:18.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When one eats\nthe Human-faced Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:24.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you become a slave to\nthe Tree of the Human-faced Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:29.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then Tokajin obeyed the order\nto turn me into fertilizer for the tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:32.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so that it would bear\nthe Fruit of Longevity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.71,0:11:35.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Master Sage, why are\nyou in that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:40.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just the fruit isn't enough\nfor longevity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:43.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The fruit must be soaked and\nmade into a potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:47.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And only I know the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:50.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I let him live\nlike that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.69,0:11:53.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:57.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So this is where you escaped to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The power of the shards is increasing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:06.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokajin is no longer human.\NPlease slay him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.81,0:12:09.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm no longer human!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.84,0:12:14.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humans are covered with mud\nand work, then grow old, then die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.48,0:12:18.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My ma and pa both lived and\ndied like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:22.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I refuse to live such a\nweak, senseless life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're not strong at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:28.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sacrifice others, just so\nyou can have longevity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way you're strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NI'm strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:35.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's why I'll take advantage\nof the weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.14,0:12:38.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you even understand that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:40.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:44.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:48.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Tree of Human-faced Fruit\nmade me strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And since I got the Sacred Jewel Shards,\NI've become invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I'll have eternal life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:57.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And turn weaklings like you\ninto fertilizer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:12:59.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.73,0:13:01.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.23,0:13:08.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wouldn't understand your logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:11.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:15.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know only too well how weak\nmortals are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.14,0:13:17.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I understand his desire\nto be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:21.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm still disgusted by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:26.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! You dare lecture me?\NIn that condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:28.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I ain't got...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:31.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,...any words for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:39.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before the Jewel Shards melt into\nthis punk's body...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:48.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Human-faced Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take a swallow of that potion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Potion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:05.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokajin made it... An imitation\nof the secret longevity potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.39,0:14:08.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's effective enough to\nheal surface wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:12.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But wouldn't drinking that make him\na slave to the Tree of Human-faced Fruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.23,0:14:16.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, you just can't eat the fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:19.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now... if you want to be saved,\ndrink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:26.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be more fun\nif you had more spunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:29.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:32.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Human-faced Fruit Tree takes\nhumans as fertilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:36.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who'd drink this disgusting stuff!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:39.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't put me in the same class as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:40.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:46.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Half-demon, you'll regret\nnot drinking the potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:50.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I don't need to drink that stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.17,0:14:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to beat the hell outta you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:55.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.65,0:15:04.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:06.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you only talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:08.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:10.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:14.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh! He can't do a thing with\na mortal body!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:17.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And with my size, the Wind Tunnel\nwon't do much good either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.03,0:15:22.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll save you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless. A bow and arrow won't\nkill Tokajin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:30.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I will kill him... without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.34,0:15:32.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just aim for the\NShikon Jewel Shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:36.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The glow of exorcism...\naround the bow and arrow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just who is this girl!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:40.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokajin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.23,0:15:48.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What... happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:54.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if the bow and arrow of\na vanquished soldier would work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.33,0:15:56.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}K- Kagome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't get... too cocky!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.48,0:16:15.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please slay Tokajin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is my way of making amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He turned into a bow and arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:31.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Old Sage... He squeezed out\nhis last ounce of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.14,0:16:33.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:39.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll tear you into bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.78,0:16:44.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can see it through\nhis back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The glow of the Jewel Shards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That glow is my target!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:02.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Sacred Jewel Shards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:09.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you... Old Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:19.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get down, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:26.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kagome!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:30.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:51.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With a mortal's body,\nyou'll die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.45,0:17:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.45,0:17:54.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}At least, if Kagome is alive...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:17:59.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:07.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:22.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh! Human-faced Fruit Tree!\NYou're rescuing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:27.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! I just don't want to lose\nprecious nourishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.73,0:18:42.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now I've attained it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The freedom of movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:49.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have ample shards of\nthe Sacred Jewel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I am all-powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:56.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then, half-demon...\nbecome one with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:06.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn... Daybreak at last!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.20,0:19:12.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd get\na half-demon as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:15.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Everything will go as planned now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:17.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.04,0:19:24.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Prepare to die, Tokajin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.21,0:19:27.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Or should I say...\NTree of the Human-faced Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.68,0:19:30.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just try, half-demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wind Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.31,0:20:01.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! We're back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:10.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokajin probably died,\nundoing his spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.39,0:20:15.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Those men in the box garden\nhave probably reverted back, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:18.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tokajin is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then Inuyasha, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:22.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:26.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When Inuyasha fell, it was\nstill dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:28.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dawn hadn't broken yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.34,0:20:30.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He probably... died...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:34.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:35.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:36.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:39.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But he was hurt badly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:43.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And no mortal could survive a\nfall from a cliff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Shippo.\NLet us pray for his repose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.13,0:20:49.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miroku...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha had no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.06,0:20:56.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wanted to save you,\neven if it cost him his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.30,0:20:59.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As if that makes me happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:07.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He had no demon power,\nyet he acted so foolishly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha was stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.32,0:21:11.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid! Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stupid Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.85,0:21:15.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What good is it\nif he's dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What am I to do from now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.22,0:21:18.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, he was foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.92,0:21:20.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha was the biggest fool\nin the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.96,0:21:25.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.30,0:21:27.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just because I'm not around...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Call me "fool" and\N"stupid," will ya!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:32.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're alive, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:37.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew you wouldn't\ndie so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:40.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.45,0:21:46.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I ain't so easy to kill!\NStop thinking rubbish!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:51.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you say "rubbish"?!\NOf course we worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.32,0:21:52.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wha...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.92,0:21:55.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We knew you were\novertaxing yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm alive, so what's the big deal?!\NStop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.43,0:21:59.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:02.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:03.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.64,0:22:04.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Am not!\N- You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:05.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Am not!\N- You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:06.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Am not!\N- You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:09.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quiet! Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:10.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:49.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ahh, Sango...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.64,0:23:53.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The three days you've been gone\nseem like a lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.05,0:23:54.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:56.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone who wants to be an apprentice\nappeared at the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:59.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They want Sango to teach them\nto become Demon Slayers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.75,0:24:01.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! They're two beautiful sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.05,0:24:04.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I envy her! Err... I mean,\nseems like hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.29,0:24:09.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"The Beautiful Sister Apprentices"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:11.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you okay, Sango?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.36,0:24:14.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Owwee!\NC'mon it's just your butt.
